title: What's The Worst First Date You've Ever Been On?
description:
First dates are nerve-racking for several reasons. All you wish is for the date to go well in hopes that a second one will follow. But what about the first dates that completely go off the rails?
It's happened to many of us. And today, we want to hear your horror stories!
